{
  "texts": [
    "Explainability is an important criterion when evaluating the current use of AI in medicine 14, 33.",
    "Because of their large number of parameters, LLMs are inherently difficult to explain.",
    "In the present study, the explainability of the results was assessed by referencing the original text of the guidelines.",
    "After the answer was evaluated as \"correct\" or \"incorrect\", the related original text of the referenced guideline content was output by the final agent.",
    "This significantly increases the explanatory power of the results."
  ]
}